Emma Navarro and Paula Badosa are scheduled to play each other in a quarterfinal matchup in the US Open Women’s Singles Tournament on September 3, 2024, at 12:00 PM ET.

This market will resolve to “Navarro” if Emma Navarro wins her match against Paula Badosa in the quarterfinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

This market will resolve to “Badosa” if Paula Badosa wins her match against Emma Navarro in the quarterfinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

If the match ends in a tie, is canceled, or delayed beyond September 10, 2024, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the US Open (ex: https://www.usopen.org/index.html) including live footage, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
